name: Will Schneider Autographed NFT Souvenir
description:
Commemorative Will Schneider autographed NFT ticket for the September 14th, 2021 screening of his 9 MFA films at The Davis Theater. Thank you for attending!
"I have spent the last 4 years of my life in DePaul's MFA program and crafting my skills as a Director. It is now time to showcase this work as I prepare to move onto the next phase of my career - feature films." -Will Schneider

Sept. 14th, 2021 Program:
E.R. A.M. (Shot in October 2018)
All a Lie (Shot in October 2020)
Goodbye Janet (Shot in November 2019)
Parricide (Shot in February 2019)
Janya (Shot in May 2021)
Graveyard (Shot in June 2021)
Malady (Shot in March 2020)
Facial (Shot in August 2020)
Ageusia (Shot in June 2019)
